{"tid":2278160,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"特朗普還輸掉夫人？英媒：梅拉尼婭正談離婚協議","createTime":"2020-11-09T03:27:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-09T03:36:15.000Z","uid":185631,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"54c8c18b9fb106022a73118eb963049a31bd3e56","tid":2278160,"uid":185631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T03:27:40.000Z","msg":"美國大選似乎告一段落，美國民主黨總統候選人拜登（Joe Biden）宣布勝出美國大選，成為第46任美國總統。美國總統特朗普不單止輸掉美國大選，還輸掉夫人。有英媒報道指，特朗普妻子梅拉尼婭正與特朗普協商離婚協議，而確保梅拉尼婭與特朗普的兒子，可以公平分配特朗普部份財產。<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》引述梅拉尼婭（Melania Trump）前顧問沃爾科夫（Stephanie Wolkoff）指，梅拉尼婭與特朗普一直分睡不同房，形容兩人關係已變成「婚姻交易」（transactional marriage）。<br />\n<br />\n沃爾科夫透露，梅拉尼婭希望在離後協議中，為兒子巴倫（Barron Trump）爭取權益，確保巴倫能夠有權公平分配特朗普部份財產。<br />\n<br />\n梅拉尼婭前員工紐曼（Omarosa Manigault Newman）亦透露，梅拉尼婭一直在倒數，只要特朗普一卸任，她就能夠離婚了。<br />\n<br />\n紐曼又指，以特朗普的性格，若特朗普在任時，梅拉尼婭提出離婚，特朗普一定不會讓她好過。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，梅拉尼婭在特朗普4年前當選時，根本沒有猜想過特朗普可勝出。當時她在特朗普當選後隔了五個月才遷入白宮，亦反映梅拉尼婭並不希望當白宮女主人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2797808/%E3%80%90%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%A7%E9%81%B8%E3%80%91%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E9%82%84%E8%BC%B8%E6%8E%89%E5%A4%AB%E4%BA%BA%EF%BC%9F%E8%8B%B1%E5%AA%92%EF%BC%9A%E6%A2%85%E6%8B%89%E5%B0%BC%E5%A9%AD%E6%AD%A3%E8%AB%87%E9%9B%A2%E5%A9%9A%E5%8D%94%E8%AD%B0?mtc=20023\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2797808%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2581%25B8%25E3%2580%2591%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2599%25AE%25E9%2582%2584%25E8%25BC%25B8%25E6%258E%2589%25E5%25A4%25AB%25E4%25BA%25BA%25EF%25BC%259F%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%25AA%2592%25EF%25BC%259A%25E6%25A2%2585%25E6%258B%2589%25E5%25B0%25BC%25E5%25A9%25AD%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E8%25AB%2587%25E9%259B%25A2%25E5%25A9%259A%25E5%258D%2594%25E8%25AD%25B0%3Fmtc%3D20023&d=FEHxtXJUwAnPMx50BANU%2BWAbrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=0d73dd1b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2797808/%E3%80%90%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%A7%E9%81%B8%E3%80%91%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E9%82%84%E8%BC%B8%E6%8E%89%E5%A4%AB%E4%BA%BA%EF%BC%9F%E8%8B%B1%E5%AA%92%EF%BC%9A%E6%A2%85%E6%8B%89%E5%B0%BC%E5%A9%AD%E6%AD%A3%E8%AB%87%E9%9B%A2%E5%A9%9A%E5%8D%94%E8%AD%B0?mtc=20023</a>"},{"pid":"6f295b32f05b8c8dfb1986b24429cdf794b54e12","tid":2278160,"uid":44209,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T03:28:52.000Z","msg":"侵侵老婆都出埋聲：美國人deserve有公平嘅選舉<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2277876\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2277876</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"306cc3b2f50b9f1546e647d99ee4cb2a174a0502","tid":2278160,"uid":222614,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T03:29:01.000Z","msg":"fake news"},{"pid":"0cbbcd3a6ee0c50a74811bdefdf88327362ed08c","tid":2278160,"uid":151074,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T03:29:27.000Z","msg":"FC 咗未"},{"pid":"9ff5f12bef4a8aebad31bf1c7b6b41d3b28436c6","tid":2278160,"uid":34869,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T03:30:00.000Z","msg":"又消息人士<br />\n咁又出到新聞唔駛FC <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56a19777812b61125bf2854f6dc4c25738fdd354","tid":2278160,"uid":125017,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T03:32:55.000Z","msg":"FC呢"},{"pid":"433e66911a62e9e763d1fea0c34322cae8c97dcb","tid":2278160,"uid":49144,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T03:33:24.000Z","msg":"fake news<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cf068fb12940b9aebc89a0d9ccdaed267771188","tid":2278160,"uid":11097,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T03:34:41.000Z","msg":"Fucking fake news<br />\nXiNN 食撚屎啦"},{"pid":"336b136f2a777430cd54339bba6bda0b11d3dcc0","tid":2278160,"uid":291128,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20